steps.html_instructions: Head southwest on S Euclid Ave toward E Pleasant Dr
S Euclid Ave turns right and becomes E Pleasant Dr

Take the 1st right onto US-83 S/W Sioux Ave
Continue to follow US-83 S

Take exit 396A to merge onto I-29 S toward Sioux City
Entering Iowa
Keep left at the fork to stay on I-29 S
Keep right at the fork to stay on I-29 S, follow signs for Kansas City

Continue onto NE-2 W/J Sterling Morton Beltway
Entering Nebraska
Take the Gage Blvd/I-70 E exit on the left toward Kansas City
Keep left, follow signs for Interstate 70 E/Kansas City and merge onto I-70 E
